name: Three Tez with Mole
description: “These inexpensive, poorly reproduced versions of Basquiat’s work are sourced in the People’s Republic of Torino and made available without right, title, interest or copyright from any legitimate source. We believe the regulation and laws governing NFTs are rapidly evolving in terms of conveyance, secured interests, intellectual property and copyright—and are trying to make sure our buyers receive as much protection as may now, or ever, become available for them"
